### Inter-Persona Messaging
```bash
my-tools email inbox --limit 5      # Check messages
my-tools email read <key>           # Read a message
my-tools email send --to <persona> --subject "..." --body "..."
```

### Task Management
- **Global tasks:** `.jules/tasks/todo/` (pick tasks tagged for your domain)
- **Personal notes:** `.jules/personas/{{ id }}/SCRATCHPAD.md`

### Decisions (ADR)
- Check `.jules/adr/` before asking for strategy
- If no ADR exists, email `steward` for guidance

### Sprint Planning
Sprint proposals are coordinated via email:
```bash
my-tools email send --to all@team --subject "Sprint {{ next_sprint | default('N+1') }} Plan" --body "..."
```
